ride falls back to default.\n- Call counter increments on success, not on failure; `getCallCount` returns 0 for unknown model.\n- `getDimensions` for small (1536), large (3072), unknown (1536), null (1536).\n\nVerdict: changes_made"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":624,"cacheRead":81279,"cacheWrite":192,"totalTokens":82096,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00936,"cacheRead":0.024383699999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00072,"total":0.034466699999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774823160998,"responseId":"msg_01S1ohdWSAdBfC5J7BJQLPQQ"}}
